# B-Admin 边界

**职责：** 萌兔 H5、`/api/Agent/srcGet|srcPost`、overrides 写入、总控 `/console`。

**可改：** `apps/admin/**`、`packages/plugin-config/**`、`data/agent-overrides/**`

**禁止：** rabbitr、gateway 出站、inject、自建 agent SPA。

**契约：** `docs/development/contracts/admin-bot.md`

**验证：** `pnpm sync:mengtu-static && pnpm --filter @wechathook/admin build && pnpm e2e:sign-alignment`
